Package: mctools
Type: Package
Title: A set of tools for Markov Chain analysis and rendering
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Fabio", family = "Caironi", email = "fabio130497@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a user-friendly shiny app for Markov Chains analysis and rendering.
    It features MC manual and file (see details) input and several outputs, including a graph and a simulation sections.
